      <div id="text-2" class="widget widget_text">
       <h3 class="widgettitle">The Bridge: Connecting Science and Policy</h3> 
       <div class="textwidget">
        <p><em>The Bridge</em> is an AGU blog that connects science and policy. It provides a platform for scientists, policy makers, and experts to communicate ideas about the science policy interface.</p> 
       </div> 
      </div>
      <div id="text-5" class="widget widget_text"> 
